{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f9e08fadb6","title":"“派代表到北京请愿是合法的”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a96ed7ac0","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"f9e08fadb6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2954c56f57","name":"吴金城"},{"id":"3061884b3a","name":"姚文生"},{"id":"4be1eeecca","name":"郭年喜"},{"id":"6c72d91291","name":"河南农学院"},{"id":"6df591b837","name":"史直人"},{"id":"af2b0c0de8","name":"王守正"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ab259b028f","type":"title","text":"“派代表到北京请愿是合法的”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"b7ac36b84f","type":"authors","text":"河南农学院吴金城史直人姚文生郭年喜王守正","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"06601a3a30","type":"paragraph","text":"吴金城（农59级学生）：林系派代表到北京请愿是合法的。杜心莲（注：右派分子）拿路费支持他们去北京没有错误。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"3eb7a24c49","type":"paragraph","text":"史直人（农59级学生）：再次要求学校给高教部拍电报（注：要求并系），否则，我们将要到北京去请愿。我们所提意见，学校不解决，我们采取有效措施——罢课。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"490d2a566f","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文生（农60级学生）：我们提出的要求是合理的，如果高教部不给答复的话，我们就罢课，拒绝实习，建议农60级十个班开会讨论不做“红色饭桶”问题。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"be1dee40c9","type":"paragraph","text":"郭年喜（林59级学生）：我不怕闹事，我兄弟多，要枪毙先枪毙我。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"05a5558c59","type":"paragraph","text":"王守正（植保教研组讲师）：在报纸上，看到处处鸣得很厉害，为什么河南不放不鸣，这恐怕是河南省委有问题。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"},{"id":"97125d02ad","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选辑》（河南农学院，1957年12月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6"}],"page":{"id":"ec7dc7db9d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f9e08fadb6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}